# AI Travel Planner

## Project Overview

AI Travel Planner is a full-stack MERN application that helps users generate AI-powered travel itineraries.

Users can enter:

- Destination
- Number of Days
- Budget Preference
- Interests

The system generates:

- Day-wise itinerary
- Budget estimation
- Hotel recommendations

The application supports multiple users with secure authentication and strict data isolation.

---

## Tech Stack

### Frontend

- React JS
- React Router DOM
- Axios
- CSS

### Backend

- Node JS
- Express JS
- MongoDB Atlas
- Mongoose

### Authentication

- JWT
- bcryptjs

### AI Integration

- Google Gemini API

---

## Features

### Authentication

- Register
- Login
- JWT Authentication
- Protected Routes

### Dashboard

- View Trips
- Delete Trips
- Create New Trips

### AI Travel Planner

Generate:

- Day-wise itinerary
- Budget estimation
- Hotel recommendations

### Authorization

Each user can only:

- View their own trips
- Create their own trips
- Delete their own trips

Users cannot access data belonging to other users.

---

## Creative Feature

### Smart Budget Estimation

The AI generates an estimated trip cost including:

- Flights
- Accommodation
- Food
- Activities

This helps travelers understand the expected cost before booking.

### Hotel Recommendations

The AI also recommends hotels based on:

- Destination
- Budget preference

This provides a more complete travel planning experience.

