---

## Authentication Flow

1. User registers
2. Password is hashed using bcrypt
3. User logs in
4. JWT token is generated
5. Token stored in cookies
6. Protected routes validate JWT token

---

## API Endpoints

### Authentication

#### Register

```http
POST /api/auth/register
```

#### Login

```http
POST /api/auth/login
```

### Profile

```http
GET /api/profile
```

### Trips

#### Generate Trip

```http
POST /api/trips/generate
```

#### Get All Trips

```http
GET /api/trips
```

#### Get Single Trip

```http
GET /api/trips/:id
```

#### Delete Trip

```http
DELETE /api/trips/:id
```

---

## Environment Variables

Backend .env

```env
PORT=5000

MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string

JWT_SECRET=your_secret

GEMINI_API_KEY=your_gemini_api_key
```

---

## Installation

### Backend

```bash
cd backend

npm install

npm run dev
```

### Frontend

```bash
cd frontend

npm install

npm start
```

---

## Deployment

### Frontend

Deployed on Vercel

Frontend URL:

https://your-frontend-url.vercel.app

### Backend

Deployed on Render

Backend URL:

https://your-backend-url.onrender.com

